NK036(chi)007:0: zab pa pod bzhi'i ngo bo nyid kyi de bas
NK036(chi)007:1: zhugs so lung med rgya gar skad du dz+aa ya
NK036(chi)007:2: a khra r+aa bod skad du grol bar byed pa'i
NK036(chi)007:3: yi ge bsdus pa zhes bya ba rtogs pa ye
NK036(chi)007:4: shes ngang la phyag 'tshal lo ston pa'i snying po
NK036(chi)007:5: rdo rje 'chang chen gyis bstan pa bsdus pa'i snying
NK036(chi)007:6: po rgyud rgyal ni bcu bdun nyid du thams cad
NK036(chi)007:7: dril nas bstan de las khyad par man ngag ngo
NK036(chi)007:8: mtshar can shin tu gsang ba'i yi ge rnams las
NK036(chi)007:9: ni gdams pa'i snying po bsdus te bcud phyung ba
NK036(chi)007:10: las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams kyi don tshig
NK036(chi)007:11: nyung yi ge bsdus pa'i don rnams kun sgom khrigs
NK036(chi)007:12: lag len nyid dang bstun nas ni bla ma rnams
NK036(chi)007:13: kyi thugs kyi gsang bcud 'di skal ldan skyes mchog
NK036(chi)007:14: snying dang 'dra ba las blo dman theg pa dman
NK036(chi)007:15: pa'i rigs can la rlung phyogs tsam du 'di nyid
NK036(chi)007:16: brjod pa med rang gi rgyud la rtag tu goms
NK036(chi)007:17: par gyis 'di las go na thabs gzhan yod re
NK036(chi)007:18: kan 'di ni dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK036(chi)007:19: snying phyung ba'o 'dir bsdus pa'i yi ge mang du
NK036(chi)007:20: yod na yang ngo mtshar can gyi gdams ngag bzhi
NK036(chi)007:21: byung ngo mtshar can gyi gdams ngag bzhi las ya
NK036(chi)007:22: mtshan can gyi tshig bzhi byung ya mtshan can gyi
NK036(chi)007:23: tshig bzhi las mthar thug pa'i don bzhi byung ba'o
NK036(chi)007:24: ngo mtshar can gyi man ngag bzhi ni kha byang
NK036(chi)007:25: dung ris ma ni bltas pa tsam gyis shes man
NK036(chi)007:26: ngag yi ge ma ru mthong ba tsam gyis rtogs
NK036(chi)007:27: gdams pa dum dum khrigs ni bklag pa tsam gyis
NK036(chi)007:28: go ngan sngags bsam le ma ni bsam pa tsam
NK036(chi)007:29: gyis 'grub ya mtshan can gyi tshig bzhi ni rgyud
NK036(chi)007:30: kyi khong snying phyung nas skal ldan mig tu bcug
NK036(chi)007:31: rig pa spar zin byas nas nam mkha'i khams su
NK036(chi)007:32: bzhag shes bya dum bur bcad nas yid kyis goms
NK036(chi)007:33: par bya rnal 'byor sngags mi smra bar mkha' 'gro
NK036(chi)007:34: bran ltar 'khol mthar thug gsang ba'i don bzhi ni
NK036(chi)007:35: mthong ma myong bar rgyud bcu bdun gyi don dang
NK036(chi)007:36: tshig skad cig la shes shing go bas gang zag
NK036(chi)007:37: gcig gdan thog gcig tu sangs rgya ba'i don dang
NK036(chi)007:38: rig pa mngon sum du bstan nas snang ba thams
NK036(chi)007:39: cad dus gcig la chod pas zag pa dang bcas
NK036(chi)007:40: pa'i phung po lhag ma med par 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK036(chi)007:41: don dang sgro 'dogs thams cad dus gcig la gcad
NK036(chi)007:42: nas shes bya rang gi 'dug tshul de nyid thams
NK036(chi)007:43: cad gtan la 'bebs pa'i don dang sngags dang gtor
NK036(chi)007:44: ma la ma brte na par rnal 'byor pa bsam
NK036(chi)007:45: pa dang ldan pas 'gal byed zla ba bdun na
NK036(chi)007:46: khrag tu skyugs nas 'chi bar byed pa'i don no
NK036(chi)007:47: de nas 'di dag ni rab tu zab par yang
NK036(chi)007:48: bstan pas gsang ba'i thig pa yang gab sbas pa'i
NK036(chi)007:50: gsang ba ngo bo nyid kyi debs rdzogs so las
NK036(chi)007:51: can gcig dang 'phrad par shog gter nas gter du
NK036(chi)007:52: btsas pa'o // man ngag brgya bcu dgu'i them byang bzhugs so //
NK036(chi)007:54: rgyud kyi dgongs pa ma yig man ngag snying po'i
NK036(chi)007:55: don brgya dang bcu dgu dag tu grangs bcad pas
NK036(chi)007:56: / gsang ba'i man ngag dum dum khrigs dang /
NK036(chi)007:58: 2 'khrug gzhi gsal ba'i me long dang 3 /
NK036(chi)007:75: 19 bsam gtan rang gnad dang nyi shu'o /
NK036(chi)007:85: lta ba'i gser bkod dang sum cu30 /
NK036(chi)007:95: dgongs don bzhi pa dang bzhi bcu40 /
NK036(chi)007:105: bsgom pa'i 'khor lo dang lnga bcu50 /
NK036(chi)007:108: spros med dbang gi man ngag dang 53 /
NK036(chi)007:115: dbang sbyor pra khrid dang drug cu /
NK036(chi)007:126: lung yig bsdus pa dang bdun cu70 /
NK036(chi)007:134: bsam gtan nyal ba'i 'khor lo dang 78 /
NK036(chi)007:145: lo rgyus chen mo 89dang dgu bcu90 /
NK036(chi)007:155: stong pa'i mtha' byed dang brgya tham pa100 /
NK036(chi)007:159: ka dag chen po'i dag yig dang 104 /
NK036(chi)007:175: rig pa'i gnas sa nyid dang 120 /
NK036(chi)007:176: mig gi bsam gtan dang bcu dagu'o121 //
NK036(chi)007:177: rtsa ba brgyad rtsa ba'i rgyud gnyis la sogs pa rdzogs pa rang byung dang yi ge med pa /
NK036(chi)007:179: go rim 'jug nges par bstan na /
NK036(chi)007:181: rtsa rgyud ni bskyed dang bshad rgyud ni rang shar
NK036(chi)007:182: dang rang grol bshad dang rin chen sprung pa sku
NK036(chi)007:184: lung dang thal 'gyur bkra shis mdzes ldan rig pa gsal ba'i rgyud /
NK036(chi)007:185: rgyud sde bzhi man ngag me long gnyis ngo sprod spras pa mu tig 'phreng ba /
NK036(chi)007:186: dgongs klong drug sgron ma 'bar ba pa dang //
NK036(chi)007:188: 'jug dang rang grol gnyis seng ge rtsal rdzogs nor bu phra bkod /
NK036(chi)007:189: mkhas pa nag mo khros skyong ba dang //
NK036(chi)007:190: mchog gi bstan pa gang zag gcig gi cha rkyen du bstan 'dzin pa dang //
NK036(chi)007:191: bsrung ba rdzogs pa rang rgyud la sogs pa /
NK036(chi)007:195: rnal 'byor chen po ni rang yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs rnal ma la /
NK036(chi)007:196: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum 'byor pas na rnal 'byor ro //
NK036(chi)007:198: chos kyi dbyings ma bcos pa'i rnal ma la /
NK036(chi)007:199: rang rig pa ye shes su 'byor pas na rnal 'byor ro //
NK036(chi)007:200: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK036(chi)007:201: chos thams cad de bzhin nyid rnal ma la /
NK036(chi)007:202: rig pa ye shes su 'byor pas na rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor zhes bya'o //
NK036(chi)007:204: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs rnal ma dang /
NK036(chi)007:205: rang gi lus ngag yid dang gsum 'byor pas na /
NK036(chi)007:206: rnal 'byoor chen po zhes ni de la bya'o //
NK036(chi)007:207: chos dbyings ma bcos rnal ma la //
NK036(chi)007:208: rang rig ye shes blos 'byor pas //
NK036(chi)007:209: shin tu rnal 'byor zhes ni de la bya'o //
NK036(chi)007:210: chos nyid ma bcos rnal ma la //
NK036(chi)007:211: rang rig ye shes blos 'byor pas //
NK036(chi)007:212: rdzogs chen rnal 'byor zhes ni de la bya'o //
